<i>verb</i>: 탐구하다 [탐구하다], 추구하다 [추구하다], 쫓아다니다 [쪼차다니다], 쫓다 [쫃따], 지향하다 [지향하다], 뒤쫓다 [뒤ː쫃따] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>탐구하다 [탐구하다]</dt><br>
<dd>search for; investigate; pursue</dd><br>
<dd>학문 등을 깊이 파고들어 연구하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To dig into and look into a field of study, etc., deeply.</dd><br>
<dt>추구하다 [추구하다]</dt><br>
<dd>pursue; seek</dd><br>
<dd>목적을 이루기 위해 계속 따르며 구하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To follow and try to find something or to achieve one's purpose.</dd><br>
<dt>쫓아다니다 [쪼차다니다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. follow</dd><br>
<dd>남의 뒤를 따라다니다.</dd><br>
<dd>To tag along with or follow another person or thing around.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pursue; chase after</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것을 찾거나 얻기 위하여 부지런히 다니다.</dd><br>
<dd>To go around diligently in order to find or attain something.</dd><br>
<dt>쫓다 [쫃따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. follow; pursue</dd><br>
<dd>앞선 것을 잡으려고 서둘러 뒤를 따르거나 자취를 따라가다.</dd><br>
<dd>To go after or follow the trace of something or someone hurriedly in order to catch.</dd><br>
<dd>2. drive out</dd><br>
<dd>떠나도록 몰아내다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make someone or something leave.</dd><br>
<dd>3. drive away</dd><br>
<dd>졸음이나 잡념 등을 물리치다.</dd><br>
<dd>To get rid of sleepiness, idle thoughts, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>지향하다 [지향하다]</dt><br>
<dd>pursue; seek</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 목적이나 목표에 뜻을 두다.</dd><br>
<dd>To strive to achieve something,</dd><br>
<dt>뒤쫓다 [뒤ː쫃따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. chase; run after; pursue</dd><br>
<dd>앞서가는 사람의 뒤를 급히 따라가다.</dd><br>
<dd>To hurriedly follow someone ahead.</dd><br>
<dd>2. kick out; throw out</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 장소에서 떠나도록 마구 몰아내다.</dd><br>
<dd>To drive someone out recklessly from a certain place.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>